
* Ubuntu 22.04 (fs_linux.py)
$GEM5/build/RISCV/gem5.fast $GEM5/configs/example/riscv/fs_linux.py --kernel=/home/ntampouratzis/COSSIM/kernels/binaries/riscv-bootloader-vmlinux-5.10-PCI --disk-image=/home/ntampouratzis/COSSIM/kernels/disks/Vitamin-V/riscv-ubuntu-node0.img --script=$GEM5/configs/boot/COSSIM/script0_riscv_standalone.rcS


* Ubuntu 22.04 (riscvmatched-fs.py)
$GEM5/build/RISCV/gem5.fast $GEM5/configs/example/gem5_library/riscvmatched-fs.py --kernel=riscv-vmlinux-6.5.5 --disk-image=riscv-ubuntu-lammps-node0.img --script=$GEM5/configs/boot/COSSIM/script0_riscv_standalone.rcS

* Ubuntu 22.04 (riscv-ubuntu-run.py)
$GEM5/build/RISCV/gem5.fast $GEM5/configs/example/gem5_library/riscv-ubuntu-run.py --kernel=riscv-vmlinux-6.5.5 --disk-image=riscv-ubuntu-lammps-node0.img --script=$GEM5/configs/boot/COSSIM/script0_riscv_standalone.rcS

* Buildroot
$GEM5/build/RISCV/gem5.fast --listener-mode=on -r -d node0 $GEM5/configs/example/riscv/fs_linux.py --kernel=/home/ntampouratzis/COSSIM/kernels/binaries/riscv-bootloader-vmlinux-5.10-PCI --disk-image=/home/ntampouratzis/COSSIM/kernels/disks/Vitamin-V/rootfs.ext4  (root=/dev/vda   working with eth0)

* Buildroot build
git clone git://git.buildroot.net/buildroot
cd buildroot/
make menuconfig
*Follow Section 4 from VOSys-Guide*
unset LD_LIBRARY_PATH
make
cd output/images

Delete 316 and change 315 to "root=/dev/vda" from /home/ntampouratzis/gem5_v22.0.0.2/gem5/configs/example/riscv/fs_linux.py


